22
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:03,760
Housekeeper, prepare hot water and gauze.

23
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:05,974
Yes.

24
00:02:05,974 --> 00:02:13,333
♫ May you also look up
to see the brilliant stars and moon ♫

25
00:02:16,289 --> 00:02:24,457
♫ No matter the endless rivers,
until you came into my life ♫

26
00:02:24,457 --> 00:02:28,544
♫ Rushed encounters in time,
with shallow fates ♫

27
