♫ Chasing time, riding the white horse ♫

49
00:04:10,173 --> 00:04:15,254
♫ Go together ♫

50
00:04:15,254 --> 00:04:18,440
♫ Love is pure and flawless in essence ♫

51
00:04:18,440 --> 00:04:20,758
You have saved me once again.

52
00:04:20,758 --> 00:04:26,441
♫ Let's be together ♫

53
00:05:09,126 --> 00:05:11,820
[Lai Luofu]

54
00:05:25,400 --> 00:05:28,320
Tears are of no use.

55
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:32,440
Of no use at all.

56
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:34,800
Huo'e cannot die in vain.

57
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:37,160
Shen Du

58
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:41,040
will receive the punishment he deserves.

59
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:46,000
Huo'e

60
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:49,440
will eventually be resurrected.

61
00:05:50,407 --> 00:05:52,080
[Cangming Hall]

62
00:05:52,080 --> 00:05:53,240
Your Majesty.

63
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,880
Your Majesty.

64
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:56,160
Overnight, throughout Xiang'an City,

65
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:57,360
the news has spread.

66
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,800
They all say that Great Chief Shen

67
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,560
was stabbed in the street by Chen Huo'e

68
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:02,240
yesterday

69
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:04,680
and was critically injured beyond cure.

70
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:09,040
Vice Minister Lai

71
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,840
claimed quite confidently

72
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:13,120
that Chen Huo'e had been executed
according to the law.

73
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:15,120
But a dignified court official

74
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,840
was unexpectedly wounded
by someone already declared dead

75
00:06:16,840 --> 00:06:19,440
right in front of the people.

76
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:22,120
This is more than just a flaw
in the pursuit and trial of the criminal.

77
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:25,880
It's practically a slap
in the face of our Dacang Dynasty.

78
00:06:25,880 --> 00:06:27,960
Your Highness,

79
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:29,920
everyone knows Vice Minister Lai's

80
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:31,920
utmost loyalty to our Dacang.

81
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:34,480
The Imperial Inspectorate commands
absolute obedience.

82
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:36,640
All this time it is

83
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:38,000
where the authority of Dacang resides.

84
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:41,200
Vice Minister Lai is the feared Black Fiend.

85
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:43,640
To enter the Imperial Inspectorate

86
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:45,040
is to comply without exception.

87
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:46,200
Now, Chen Huo'e

88
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:49,120
has escaped from the Imperial Inspectorate
time and again.

89
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:51,440
It is hard not to doubt

90
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:54,040
Vice Minister Lai's role in this matter,

91
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,880
whether it is due to incompetence

92
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:58,320
or deliberate aggravation.

93
00:06:58,840 --> 00:07:00,200
Your Majesty, I beg for your discernment.

94
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,520
Chen Huo'e indeed perished in custody
of the Imperial Inspectorate

95
00:07:01,520 --> 00:07:03,040
from torture interrogation.

96
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:05,200
The trial records and Chen Huo'e's confession
and personal effects

97
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:07,400
have all been submitted.

98
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:08,960
But I have heard

99
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:10,720
though Chen Huo'e was beheaded,

100
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:12,920
she still possesses the ability to resurrect.

101
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:14,560
The people are spreading rumors

102
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,320
that one day Chen Huo'e

103
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:17,760
will return.

104
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:20,120
Nonsensical talk.

105
00:07:20,880 --> 00:07:22,080
Madam Xu,

106
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:24,120
bring it out.

107
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:30,440
Great Chief of the Imperial Guards, Shen Du,
respectfully reports.

108
00:07:30,440 --> 00:07:32,320
I have captured Chen Huo'e.

109
00:07:32,320 --> 00:07:35,000
She is a rare mirror image person.

110
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:37,600
She was apprehended and beheaded on the spot.

111
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:41,560
There is no longer a Chen Huo'e in this world.

112
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:43,640
Mirror image person?

113
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:44,680
Could this be

114
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:45,920
the secret of Chen Huo'e's

115
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:48,640
repeated escapes?

116
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:51,360
Vice Minister Lai, you personally conducted
the interrogation.

117
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:55,000
Yet you failed to discover the anomaly
of Chen Huo'e's mirror image.

118
00:07:59,080 --> 00:08:01,360
I was negligent.

119
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,640
Were you negligent

120
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:07,040
or did you think

121
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:10,080
there was no need to report to me?

122
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,680
I wouldn't dare.

123
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:13,800
I would rather die a thousand deaths

124
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:17,120
than dare to conceal anything
from Your Majesty.

125
00:08:18,640 --> 00:08:19,840
It seems

126
00:08:19,840 --> 00:08:22,200
the majesty of Dacang

127
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:24,080
needs a change.

128
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:27,200
Vice Minister Lai,
you've let the criminal off the hook.

129
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:28,560
Although it was unintentional,

130
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:31,000
it was a crime of negligence.

131
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:32,360
Your salary will be docked for one year.

132
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:33,919
You should also do away

133
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:36,080
with that usual entourage of yours

134
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:38,280
when going out.

135
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:43,559
Thank Your Majesty for your mercy.

136
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:45,360
Madam Xu,

137
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:47,480
arrange for the best imperial physician

138
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,640
and the finest medicine

139
00:08:48,640 --> 00:08:52,760
to ensure that Minister Shen
makes a speedy recovery.

140
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:55,912
Yes.

141
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:01,400
Having made such a grave mistake,

142
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:03,280
he is merely docked a year's salary.

143
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:04,600
Mother Empress truly

144
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:06,240
shows favoritism towards Vice Minister Lai.

145
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,800
If Your Highness have an objection,

146
00:09:07,800 --> 00:09:11,200
why didn't you bring it up
in the court earlier?

147
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,520
Prime Minister Zhang, what do you mean?

148
00:09:12,520 --> 00:09:14,856
Prime Minister Zhang.

149
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:18,200
Your Highness.

150
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,840
Chen Huo'e has committed heinous crimes.

151
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:22,200
Our Mother Empress made her own decision.

152
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:25,200
We'd better not to discuss it here.

153
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:27,680
Prince Xian makes a fair point.

154
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:31,240
I was rash.

155
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:34,440
It's just you who likes to play the good guy.

156
00:10:35,760 --> 00:10:38,320
You've lost so much blood

157
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:40,760
and had a high fever last night.

158
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:44,360
You must wake up.

159
00:10:45,040 --> 00:10:48,360
I haven't yet helped your Shen family
overturn the case.

160
00:10:59,446 --> 00:11:02,421
♫ Heart burnt once,
a body lonesome and withered ♫

161
00:11:02,421 --> 00:11:06,422
♫ A lifetime of solitude ♫

162
00:11:06,422 --> 00:11:09,666
♫ Love once burned, where has it scattered ♫

163
00:11:09,666 --> 00:11:13,110
♫ The mottles ♫

164
00:11:13,110 --> 00:11:16,840
♫ Drifting in the mist ♫

165
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,240
Why have you come again?

166
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,600
If you're caught, you'll lose your life.

167
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:23,160
I promised to bring you

168
00:11:23,160 --> 00:11:25,440
the kickball-shaped pastries
from the West Market.

169
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:28,680
Although they got a bit squashed
on the way here,

170
00:11:28,680 --> 00:11:31,320
the taste should still be good.

171
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:33,928
Quick, have a taste.

172
00:11:34,774 --> 00:11:41,270
♫ Love is elusive,
stinging you and scorching me ♫

173
00:11:41,270 --> 00:11:45,642
♫ Along the way,
flowers bloom and fall, heavy rain pours ♫

174
00:11:45,642 --> 00:11:49,590
♫ Lights will intertwine ♫

175
00:11:49,590 --> 00:11:54,876
♫ You are my final destination ♫

176
00:11:55,382 --> 00:11:58,291
♫ Who will guide me through loneliness
and confusion ♫

177
00:11:58,291 --> 00:12:02,960
♫ Understand my vulnerability.
No need for words ♫

178
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:04,560
I don't have any money on me.

179
00:12:04,560 --> 00:12:06,080
Let me give this to you.

180
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:08,120
I don't want your money.

181
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:11,400
Do you think I'm a servant delivering dishes?

182
00:12:11,400 --> 00:12:13,720
No. I…

183
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:15,640
This whistle was given to me by my dad.

184
00:12:15,640 --> 00:12:18,840
Look, there's the character "Shen" on it.

185
00:12:23,574 --> 00:12:28,000
♫ Who will guide me through right and wrong ♫

186
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:29,160
I'll go first.

187
00:12:29,160 --> 00:12:30,600
Otherwise, they'll come to catch me again.

188
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:33,528
♫ Who will guide me through grudges and karma ♫

189
00:12:33,528 --> 00:12:36,560
♫ Soothe my sense of loss, never to escape ♫

190
00:12:36,560 --> 00:12:38,760
Will you come back?

191
00:12:40,160 --> 00:12:41,240
Of course.

192
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,640
Someday

193
00:12:42,640 --> 00:12:44,400
I will overturn the case for the Shen family

194
00:12:44,400 --> 00:12:47,480
and take you out with honor and integrity.

195
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:56,040
When you were in the detention center,

196
00:12:56,040 --> 00:12:57,200
it was such a difficult situation

197
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:59,000
and you could get through it.

198
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:00,680
This time,

199
00:13:00,680 --> 00:13:03,720
you can surely turn misfortune
into fortune too.

200
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:06,920
So it really was you.

201
00:13:16,400 --> 00:13:18,360
You will.

202
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:20,872
You will.

203
00:13:22,080 --> 00:13:23,520
Great Chief Shen,

204
00:13:23,520 --> 00:13:25,320
even if you are sick,

205
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:27,480
you must stay spirited.

206
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:29,560
Change into some fresh clothing.

207
00:13:29,560 --> 00:13:33,520
Perhaps it could speed up the recovery.

208
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:47,240
Fortunately, it was you.

209
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:10,200
I've stitched up the wound.

210
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:13,720
He's lying here

211
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:16,680
just like any other corpse.

212
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:21,640
I've dissected so many male corpses.

213
00:14:21,640 --> 00:14:24,240
Am I afraid to change his clothes?

214
00:15:02,160 --> 00:15:03,680
He places this wicker piglet under his pillow

215
00:15:03,680 --> 00:15:06,120
every night.

216
00:15:06,120 --> 00:15:08,120
The handwriting on the letter
is delicate and graceful.

217
00:15:08,120 --> 00:15:13,400
It must come from the woman he can't forget.

218
00:15:18,640 --> 00:15:20,360
Rest assured.

219
00:15:20,360 --> 00:15:23,000
I won't cling to you.

220
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:24,520
You saved me.

221
00:15:24,520 --> 00:15:26,680
I took care of you.

222
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:30,240
We are even now.

223
00:15:31,120 --> 00:15:33,560
When the three months are up,

224
00:15:34,560 --> 00:15:37,480
I will divorce you as promised.

225
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:46,360
Three months.

226
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:49,840
Divorce as promised?

227
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:52,200
What did I hear?

228
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:54,880
- Chuichui.
- Liuniang.

229
00:15:54,880 --> 00:15:56,960
How did you get here?

230
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:00,280
Such a big thing happened.

231
00:16:00,280 --> 00:16:02,600
How could I not come?

232
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:03,960
After this morning's court session,

233
00:16:03,960 --> 00:16:05,440
all Six Ministries are talking about it.

234
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:08,520
The White Ghost was fatally wounded
by Chen Huo'e.

235
00:16:08,520 --> 00:16:11,040
Is he going to pass away?

236
00:16:11,040 --> 00:16:13,600
He is badly injured, but…

237
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:14,640
But what?

238
00:16:14,640 --> 00:16:16,280
You're going to worry me to death.

239
00:16:16,280 --> 00:16:17,480
Liuniang,

240
00:16:17,480 --> 00:16:20,200
what exactly happened
between you and White Ghost?

241
00:16:21,520 --> 00:16:22,800
Nothing.

242
00:16:22,800 --> 00:16:25,760
At this point, you still want
to hide it from me?

243
00:16:25,760 --> 00:16:29,120
You two are a fake couple?

244
00:16:30,800 --> 00:16:34,160
Chuichui, you must keep this a secret for me.

245
00:16:34,160 --> 00:16:36,440
I had no other choice.

246
00:16:36,440 --> 00:16:38,840
Did Shen Du threaten you?

247
00:16:38,840 --> 00:16:41,120
Most certainly.

248
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:43,440
Three months.

249
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:45,880
Then you could escape

250
00:16:45,880 --> 00:16:48,240
from the White Ghost's lair?

251
00:16:48,240 --> 00:16:50,640
That would be a good thing.

252
00:16:52,880 --> 00:16:54,080
But,

253
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:56,040
in his current condition,

254
00:16:56,040 --> 00:16:58,160
what if he won't wake up in three months?

255
00:16:58,160 --> 00:16:59,360
It won't happen.

256
00:16:59,360 --> 00:17:00,400
He will definitely wake up.

257
00:17:00,400 --> 00:17:02,080
But what if he won't wake up?

258
00:17:02,080 --> 00:17:03,360
Will you just keep guarding him like this?

259
00:17:03,360 --> 00:17:05,480
He became like this trying to save me.

260
00:17:05,480 --> 00:17:06,599
Yes, I know.

261
00:17:06,599 --> 00:17:09,119
But you have to think for yourself.

262
00:17:09,119 --> 00:17:11,528
In case,

263
00:17:12,040 --> 00:17:14,839
he…

264
00:17:14,839 --> 00:17:16,480
Will you just keep living like a widow for him?

265
00:17:16,480 --> 00:17:17,800
Bah. What nonsense are you talking about?

266
00:17:17,800 --> 00:17:19,480
- You say bah.
- Bah.

267
00:17:19,480 --> 00:17:21,599
Since the two of you are a fake couple,

268
00:17:21,599 --> 00:17:23,599
no matter what happens to him,

269
00:17:23,599 --> 00:17:25,800
you have to plan for yourself.

270
00:17:25,800 --> 00:17:26,880
Just think,

271
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:28,840
when you return
to the Yan Mansion in the future,

272
00:17:28,840 --> 00:17:31,320
if you end up as a divorced woman,

273
00:17:31,320 --> 00:17:33,440
your family's madame

274
00:17:33,440 --> 00:17:35,280
along with your siblings,

275
00:17:35,280 --> 00:17:37,000
will they still give you good days to live?

276
00:17:37,000 --> 00:17:38,280
Wouldn't you and Lady Jin

277
00:17:38,280 --> 00:17:41,920
be subjected every day
to all kinds of disdain and exclusion?

278
00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:43,280
I think it's better for you

279
00:17:43,280 --> 00:17:46,400
to find another good man to remarry.

280
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:47,600
No, Chuichui,

281
00:17:47,600 --> 00:17:48,920
what are you talking about?

282
00:17:48,920 --> 00:17:51,208
The Ministry of Justice.

283
00:17:53,080 --> 00:17:56,640
I think the Ministry of Justice seems
to have no good men to remarry.

284
00:17:58,760 --> 00:18:00,000
Jiang Langxing.

285
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:02,640
Why not consider Jiang Langxing?

286
00:18:02,640 --> 00:18:04,640
Although Jiang Langxing

287
00:18:04,640 --> 00:18:05,960
always

288
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:08,200
has a sour face

289
00:18:08,200 --> 00:18:09,800
and behaves properly,

290
00:18:09,800 --> 00:18:12,560
he truly is a good man.

291
00:18:12,560 --> 00:18:15,360
At times, he's quite adorable. He is good.

292
00:18:15,360 --> 00:18:18,320
You want to set me up with Jiang Langxing?

293
00:18:18,320 --> 00:18:20,744
Isn't he good?

294
00:18:22,040 --> 00:18:25,600
Alright. I'll think about it some more.

295
00:18:26,720 --> 00:18:27,800
I've thought

296
00:18:27,800 --> 00:18:30,320
of a more suitable candidate.

297
00:18:30,320 --> 00:18:32,400
Marshal Inspector.

298
00:18:33,320 --> 00:18:34,960
Although Marshal Xu

299
00:18:34,960 --> 00:18:37,320
comes from humble origins,

300
00:18:37,320 --> 00:18:39,480
he is tall and imposing

301
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:41,560
and has a generous character.

302
00:18:41,560 --> 00:18:42,760
If you can't become

303
00:18:42,760 --> 00:18:44,400
the lady of the Shen family,

304
00:18:44,400 --> 00:18:46,040
being Marshal Inspector's wife

305
00:18:46,040 --> 00:18:48,680
would also carry great prestige.

306
00:18:48,680 --> 00:18:50,640
Mr. Xu is a good man,

307
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:52,800
but I have no personal feelings for him.

308
00:18:52,800 --> 00:18:54,640
Chuichui, please don't keep playing
matchmaker anymore.

309
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:56,680
Affection can be cultivated.

310
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:57,880
From Marshal Xu's appearance,

311
00:18:57,880 --> 00:18:59,240
at first glance, he is

312
00:18:59,240 --> 00:19:00,640
someone who would dote on his wife.

313
00:19:00,640 --> 00:19:02,200
That's so much better.

314
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:03,920
That's better than being with the White Ghost

315
00:19:03,920 --> 00:19:06,920
who annoys you all day long.

316
00:19:09,560 --> 00:19:12,080
I am only injured,

317
00:19:12,080 --> 00:19:14,200
not dead.

318
00:19:15,920 --> 00:19:16,920
Shen Du.

319
00:19:16,920 --> 00:19:18,080
You are awake.

320
00:19:18,080 --> 00:19:19,760
Take it slow.

321
00:19:19,760 --> 00:19:22,088
Lu Chuichui,

322
00:19:23,160 --> 00:19:24,680
it's not your place to run to my mansion

323
00:19:24,680 --> 00:19:26,920
and point fingers.

324
00:19:30,400 --> 00:19:32,808
Get out!

325
00:19:36,200 --> 00:19:38,200
Liuniang,

326
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:39,200
I'll wait for you outside.

327
00:19:39,200 --> 00:19:41,800
You…

328
00:19:41,800 --> 00:19:44,072
Slow down.

329
00:19:44,920 --> 00:19:47,440
You…

330
00:19:47,440 --> 00:19:49,960
When did you wake up?

331
00:19:59,240 --> 00:20:00,920
Just now.

332
00:20:00,920 --> 00:20:03,368
Just now?

333
00:20:04,280 --> 00:20:06,040
You just

334
00:20:06,040 --> 00:20:07,040
suddenly…

335
00:20:07,040 --> 00:20:09,800
I just woke up all of a sudden.

336
00:20:26,120 --> 00:20:28,584
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

337
00:20:35,560 --> 00:20:37,720
If it weren't for you,

338
00:20:37,720 --> 00:20:41,480
I would have died at the hands of Chen Huo'e.

339
00:20:41,480 --> 00:20:44,240
You got so seriously injured because of it.

340
00:20:48,520 --> 00:20:50,880
It's Chen Huo'e who was wrong,

341
00:20:50,880 --> 00:20:53,256
not you.

342
00:20:55,240 --> 00:20:57,600
Weren't these injuries on me

343
00:20:57,600 --> 00:20:59,880
treated by you?

344
00:21:08,800 --> 00:21:11,320
Where's the body of Chen Huo'e?

345
00:21:11,320 --> 00:21:13,120
At the time, you were injured.

346
00:21:13,120 --> 00:21:15,400
Jing Lin and I rushed to bring you back.

347
00:21:15,400 --> 00:21:17,040
The corpse of Chen Huo'e

348
00:21:17,040 --> 00:21:18,640
was secretly taken away by someone.

349
00:21:18,640 --> 00:21:20,360
Jing Lin went to investigate overnight

350
00:21:20,360 --> 00:21:22,280
and speculated that it was someone
from the Imperial Inspectorate

351
00:21:22,280 --> 00:21:25,200
who took her corpse.

352
00:21:25,200 --> 00:21:27,240
Lai Luozhi.

353
00:21:28,640 --> 00:21:30,600
I'm thinking,

354
00:21:30,600 --> 00:21:32,880
Chen Huo'e's previous disappearance

355
00:21:32,880 --> 00:21:34,800
was a dereliction of duty by Lai Luozhi.

356
00:21:34,800 --> 00:21:36,160
Now the people from the Imperial Inspectorate

357
00:21:36,160 --> 00:21:38,640
have stolen Chen Huo'e's corpse.

358
00:21:38,640 --> 00:21:41,120
I'm afraid there must be a scheme.

359
00:21:41,120 --> 00:21:42,720
We might as well wait a bit.

360
00:21:42,720 --> 00:21:44,080
Use stillness to control action.

361
00:21:44,080 --> 00:21:47,280
Let's see what move they will make.

362
00:22:03,760 --> 00:22:06,440
You should rest well first.

363
00:22:36,200 --> 00:22:37,360
Housekeeper.

364
00:22:37,360 --> 00:22:39,160
The Great Chief has already woken up.

365
00:22:39,160 --> 00:22:40,640
Go quickly and ask
the physician to take a look.

366
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:43,000
My Lord has awoken.

367
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:45,120
Thank goodness.

368
00:22:45,120 --> 00:22:48,240
Quick, go call the physician.

369
00:23:00,600 --> 00:23:02,640
Liuniang.

370
00:23:02,640 --> 00:23:04,120
Chuichui.

371
00:23:04,120 --> 00:23:06,280
You have finally come out.

372
00:23:06,280 --> 00:23:08,560
You go manage these people of the Shen Mansion.

373
00:23:08,560 --> 00:23:09,960
Mrs. Shen's good friend is here.

374
00:23:09,960 --> 00:23:11,680
Not even providing me with a meal.

375
00:23:11,680 --> 00:23:13,680
Miss Lu,

376
00:23:13,680 --> 00:23:16,160
are you lacking silver?

377
00:23:17,440 --> 00:23:18,720
You don't know.

378
00:23:18,720 --> 00:23:20,000
The new plays at the Furong Garden

379
00:23:20,000 --> 00:23:21,520
are really good.

380
00:23:21,520 --> 00:23:24,800
The actor's performance is absolutely stunning.

381
00:23:24,800 --> 00:23:27,120
I just

382
00:23:27,120 --> 00:23:30,760
used my pocket money to tip them.

383
00:23:30,760 --> 00:23:32,360
My father has cut off

384
00:23:32,360 --> 00:23:33,560
my pocket money.

385
00:23:33,560 --> 00:23:36,640
And this month's allowance
hasn't been issued yet.

386
00:23:36,640 --> 00:23:39,040
Well,

387
00:23:39,720 --> 00:23:41,200
we are besties.

388
00:23:41,200 --> 00:23:43,480
Just say whether you'll take care
of the meal or not.

389
00:23:45,840 --> 00:23:47,400
Mr. Shen.

390
00:23:47,400 --> 00:23:49,440
Coming.

391
00:23:50,080 --> 00:23:51,440
What's your order?

392
00:23:51,440 --> 00:23:53,640
Please arrange for Chuichui and Miss Yun Que

393
00:23:53,640 --> 00:23:55,440
to have their meals.

394
00:23:55,440 --> 00:23:56,480
Prepare another meal box.

395
00:23:56,480 --> 00:23:58,320
- I will take it to the main bedroom.
- Alright.

396
00:23:58,320 --> 00:23:59,640
Yan Liuniang,

397
00:23:59,640 --> 00:24:01,720
we rarely get to have a meal together.

398
00:24:01,720 --> 00:24:03,600
Won't you join me?

399
00:24:03,600 --> 00:24:05,120
Shen Du is bedridden with injuries.

400
00:24:05,120 --> 00:24:06,680
He just woke up and can't be left alone.

401
00:24:06,680 --> 00:24:08,440
There are so many people in the Shen Mansion.

402
00:24:08,440 --> 00:24:11,080
They won't miss one person.

403
00:24:26,960 --> 00:24:28,840
Yun Que,

404
00:24:28,840 --> 00:24:31,800
weren't you the one claiming
that you would marry the White…?

405
00:24:32,880 --> 00:24:35,160
Shen Du?

406
00:24:35,160 --> 00:24:36,680
Shen Du was seriously injured.

407
00:24:36,680 --> 00:24:38,440
You're not going to claim your merits.

408
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:41,000
Instead, you're here seeking tranquility.

409
00:24:46,000 --> 00:24:47,200
I see through it.

410
00:24:47,200 --> 00:24:49,440
You see through it?

411
00:24:49,440 --> 00:24:50,840
She sees through it.

412
00:24:50,840 --> 00:24:53,080
The White Ghost is not a good person?

413
00:24:53,080 --> 00:24:54,760
Not a good match?

414
00:24:54,760 --> 00:24:57,680
During this time, I have indeed seen
one thing clearly.

415
00:24:57,680 --> 00:24:58,680
Yan Xing,

416
00:24:58,680 --> 00:25:00,040
your ambition lies not with being Mrs. Shen.

417
00:25:00,040 --> 00:25:02,160
Why spend a lifetime at the Shen Mansion?

418
00:25:02,160 --> 00:25:04,640
Well said.

419
00:25:04,640 --> 00:25:06,440
You two are still in the Shen Mansion.

420
00:25:06,440 --> 00:25:08,520
Keep your voices down.

421
00:25:13,240 --> 00:25:16,840
Madam, the food you want is ready.

422
00:25:42,520 --> 00:25:44,872
Servant!

423
00:25:46,360 --> 00:25:48,320
At your service.

424
00:25:48,320 --> 00:25:49,560
Carry out my orders.

425
00:25:49,560 --> 00:25:51,960
Now that they have entered the game,

426
00:25:51,960 --> 00:25:54,120
let's add

427
00:25:54,120 --> 00:25:56,280
a bit more spice to it.

428
00:26:10,880 --> 00:26:12,880
Right?

429
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:19,680
Let me tell you, he really is super handsome.

430
00:26:19,680 --> 00:26:22,520
You're absolutely right.

431
00:26:23,120 --> 00:26:25,280
In just the time it takes for a meal,

432
00:26:25,280 --> 00:26:28,760
you two have become so intimate.

433
00:26:28,760 --> 00:26:31,760
My meeting with Yun Que was very joyful.

434
00:26:31,760 --> 00:26:33,120
As if we were old friends at first sight.

435
00:26:33,120 --> 00:26:34,760
Close like sisters.

436
00:26:34,760 --> 00:26:36,480
Chuichui and I both believe

437
00:26:36,480 --> 00:26:38,520
that only women truly understand women.

438
00:26:38,520 --> 00:26:41,040
Our fate should not be decided by others.

439
00:26:41,040 --> 00:26:44,880
Exactly, we should find our own path forward.

440
00:26:44,880 --> 00:26:47,040
Therefore, we have decided

441
00:26:47,040 --> 00:26:48,880
to invite you to join us in three days

442
00:26:48,880 --> 00:26:51,840
to seek marriage fate together
at Mingsheng Temple.

443
00:26:51,840 --> 00:26:52,880
Mingsheng Temple?

444
00:26:52,880 --> 00:26:54,880
Praying for a marriage match?

445
00:26:55,680 --> 00:26:58,160
You don't really want

446
00:26:58,160 --> 00:27:00,960
to be Mrs. Shen
for the rest of your life, do you?

447
00:27:00,960 --> 00:27:02,920
Although I've lost interest in Shen Du,

448
00:27:02,920 --> 00:27:06,920
could it be that you and Shen Du
are really a harmonious couple?

449
00:27:06,920 --> 00:27:09,280
The three-month agreement no longer counts?

450
00:27:09,280 --> 00:27:11,160
Of course, it counts.

451
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:13,480
Then why are you hesitating?

452
00:27:15,760 --> 00:27:17,680
You couldn't be

453
00:27:17,680 --> 00:27:20,480
in love with the White Ghost, could you?

454
00:27:26,280 --> 00:27:28,360
When the agreed time comes,

455
00:27:28,360 --> 00:27:30,880
I will naturally leave him.

456
00:27:32,280 --> 00:27:34,120
I am only focused on career and reputation.

457
00:27:34,120 --> 00:27:37,080
I haven't thought about remarriage.

458
00:27:37,080 --> 00:27:39,120
Marital fate and career success
are not mutually exclusive.

459
00:27:39,120 --> 00:27:40,520
Exactly.

460
00:27:40,520 --> 00:27:43,000
Three days later, we'll go
to Mingsheng Temple first

461
00:27:43,000 --> 00:27:44,520
and pray for a marriage match.

462
00:27:44,520 --> 00:27:46,800
It's settled then.

463
00:27:46,800 --> 00:27:49,480
Oh right. In my room, there are
freshly pickled fruits.

464
00:27:49,480 --> 00:27:51,600
I don't feel like eating recently.
Please go try some.

465
00:27:51,600 --> 00:27:52,600
I want to eat them.

466
00:27:52,600 --> 00:27:54,560
Let's go.

467
00:27:54,560 --> 00:27:57,200
We're leaving. Don't miss me too much.

468
00:29:07,360 --> 00:29:09,840
So much consideration.

469
00:29:09,840 --> 00:29:12,400
Do you want me to choose for you?

470
00:29:17,840 --> 00:29:19,320
What?

471
00:29:19,320 --> 00:29:21,520
Do you want me to help you choose?

472
00:29:30,240 --> 00:29:31,760
That's true.

473
00:29:31,760 --> 00:29:33,680
You are seriously injured now.

474
00:29:33,680 --> 00:29:36,640
It's really not proper for me
to leave you and go out.

475
00:29:38,480 --> 00:29:39,480
Later, I will

476
00:29:39,480 --> 00:29:40,560
send those few dresses

477
00:29:40,560 --> 00:29:41,560
to Chuichui

478
00:29:41,560 --> 00:29:43,040
and let her choose for herself.

479
00:29:43,040 --> 00:29:45,760
I won't be going after three days.

480
00:29:45,760 --> 00:29:48,720
The dress is chosen for Lu Chuichui?

481
00:29:48,720 --> 00:29:50,000
Right.

482
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:52,200
She has been staying at the Shen Mansion
for the past few days.

483
00:29:52,200 --> 00:29:53,680
It's a pity

484
00:29:53,680 --> 00:29:54,720
that the colors of my dresses

485
00:29:54,720 --> 00:29:56,400
are all not bright enough.

486
00:29:56,400 --> 00:29:58,880
I'm afraid she won't like them.

487
00:30:01,560 --> 00:30:04,240
Since you will go out with besties,

488
00:30:04,240 --> 00:30:06,480
you don't have to worry about me.

489
00:30:06,480 --> 00:30:09,400
The Shen Mansion is not without people
to rely on.

490
00:30:09,400 --> 00:30:11,560
As for three days from now,

491
00:30:12,880 --> 00:30:14,880
I should be able to get out of bed by then.

492
00:30:14,880 --> 00:30:16,080
I will join you at that time.

493
00:30:16,080 --> 00:30:18,240
No need. You've suffered such a serious injury.

494
00:30:18,240 --> 00:30:19,680
You need to rest a bit longer
before you'll be okay.

495
00:30:19,680 --> 00:30:21,760
You rest first, okay?

496
00:31:18,520 --> 00:31:20,640
Isn't it just because I watched
a couple of extra plays?

497
00:31:20,640 --> 00:31:23,120
How did I fall asleep?

498
00:31:24,240 --> 00:31:25,240
It must've been that

499
00:31:25,240 --> 00:31:26,640
that play was just too captivating.

500
00:31:26,640 --> 00:31:29,240
Then, I just…

501
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:34,360
It's fine.

502
00:31:36,840 --> 00:31:38,240
Today really is

503
00:31:38,240 --> 00:31:39,960
bright and sunny

504
00:31:39,960 --> 00:31:42,400
with a clear sky as far as the eye can see.

505
00:31:52,680 --> 00:31:54,800
Oh no.

506
00:31:59,480 --> 00:32:01,480
Is it a human or a ghost?

507
00:32:01,480 --> 00:32:03,656
It's a ghost.

508
00:32:04,560 --> 00:32:06,480
What's there to fear about ghosts?

509
00:32:06,480 --> 00:32:09,080
They were all people before they died.

510
00:32:09,080 --> 00:32:12,400
You're not scared, but I am!

511
00:32:13,040 --> 00:32:15,520
If it's a ghost, I'd be scared to death.

512
00:32:15,520 --> 00:32:17,000
Every grievance has its perpetrator,
every debt its debtor.

513
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:19,080
Whoever owes you, go find them.

514
00:32:19,080 --> 00:32:20,320
I'm begging you, please go away.

515
00:32:20,320 --> 00:32:21,640
I'm begging you, please go away.

516
00:32:21,640 --> 00:32:23,920
Back at the cemetery,

517
00:32:23,920 --> 00:32:25,320
how come I didn't notice

518
00:32:25,320 --> 00:32:27,560
that you were such a scaredy-cat?

519
00:32:30,600 --> 00:32:33,288
Oh, it's you!

520
00:32:37,680 --> 00:32:38,840
Mr. Mask,

521
00:32:38,840 --> 00:32:40,240
it's so strange.

522
00:32:40,240 --> 00:32:42,760
I was so scared just a moment ago.

523
00:32:42,760 --> 00:32:44,640
But as soon as you sit beside me,

524
00:32:44,640 --> 00:32:45,840
suddenly this place seems

525
00:32:45,840 --> 00:32:47,520
not so scary anymore.

526
00:32:47,520 --> 00:32:49,440
Perhaps it's because

527
00:32:49,440 --> 00:32:52,000
all the ghosts and ghouls here
are afraid of me.

528
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:54,400
Why do you belittle yourself?

529
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:57,400
It's just a fact.

530
00:32:57,400 --> 00:32:58,680
In this world,

531
00:32:58,680 --> 00:33:00,600
not to mention people,

532
00:33:00,600 --> 00:33:02,760
even all evil spirits and ghosts

533
00:33:02,760 --> 00:33:05,240
fear to not escape me in time.

534
00:33:05,240 --> 00:33:06,760
You're talking nonsense.

535
00:33:06,760 --> 00:33:08,920
Why do you have to say something so scary?

536
00:33:08,920 --> 00:33:11,320
You're clearly so good.

537
00:33:12,840 --> 00:33:14,040
Look.

538
00:33:14,040 --> 00:33:15,360
It's just like

539
00:33:15,360 --> 00:33:16,400
in this void,

540
00:33:16,400 --> 00:33:18,320
the invisible little fairies

541
00:33:18,320 --> 00:33:20,760
all want to be your friends.

542
00:33:20,760 --> 00:33:23,272
If you don't believe me, look.

543
00:33:24,280 --> 00:33:26,792
Watch carefully.

544
00:33:37,360 --> 00:33:39,560
Little fairy.

545
00:33:39,560 --> 00:33:41,040
Would you like to be friends

546
00:33:41,040 --> 00:33:43,200
with Mr. Mask?

547
00:33:43,960 --> 00:33:45,600
If you're willing,

548
00:33:45,600 --> 00:33:46,880
just jump from this bowl

